{"tid":2514333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚驚 有冇巴打教我應該點做","createTime":"2021-05-03T07:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T08:18:19.000Z","uid":97419,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e947208de8fe2e04aa4d425cd074addf34f83984","tid":2514333,"uid":97419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:47:48.000Z","msg":"小弟住公屋 本身屋邨有維修承辦商<br />\n啱啱有個男人話要入嚟油防水油<br />\n又講得出間公司名 show埋啲證明又乜又乜<br />\n我就話唔洗油 但佢話睇一睇 比個交待比公司<br />\n咁佢入左黎2秒睇一睇就話唔洗<br />\n我諗諗下唔撚對路 打落下面辦事處問<br />\n點知佢話完全冇呢個工程要做<br />\n諗起最近好多入屋爆竊案 即刻出門口睇吓有冇咩記號<br />\n但係又乜都冇<br />\n請問各路大神我係咪比人探撚左路<br />\n應該點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2579add50a64db2bdd5a9694eafeeaf3114c1ab","tid":2514333,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:50:50.000Z","msg":"報定狗"},{"pid":"805d2dc35dcfe73ee6ba4744a0ed3410502f6c09","tid":2514333,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:53:34.000Z","msg":"加鎖加cam"},{"pid":"83c33e9c63ba6a635dd9550b37312e11ddbd6a7a","tid":2514333,"uid":97419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2579add50a64db2bdd5a9694eafeeaf3114c1ab","tid":2514333,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:50:50.000Z","msg":"報定狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我老竇話可能係承辦商判咗俾人做"},{"pid":"a5e2e8a83cc33a3e61adfef5e8fcc5f5583d32d3","tid":2514333,"uid":97419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:02:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3af0bcf44a3061c8b324b8af5247024ea5fa62d9","tid":2514333,"uid":97419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eec8543b3f0f43b102710650fd0aa05e7230d8a6","tid":2514333,"uid":97419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T08:02:51.000Z"